OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate sunny
OL,6,Fspells, then, especially for Orkney,
OL,7,Fclear spells overnight with showers.
OL,8,FCloudier for Shetland, perhaps more
OL,9,Fpersistent rain, through the early
OL,10,Fhours. Strong northerly breeze, risk
OL,11,Fof gales Shetland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAny rain across Shetland soon
OL,14,Fclearing then a bright, but cold, day
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells and a few showers.
OL,16,FStrong northerly or northwesterly
OL,17,Fwinds slowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
