OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells Saturday with
OL,7,Fnorthwesterly winds easing. Morning
OL,8,Frain Sunday but becoming brighter for
OL,9,Fthe afternoon with a few showers.
OL,10,FRather cloudy Monday with rain at
OL,11,Ftimes.
